[{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"# Deploying the Model\n\nThe training and test tables as well as the models' scoring materials have been built in previous steps.\n\nIn case you have not followed previous steps, you need, at least, to run the following SAS notebook:\n\n**sas-education/sas1/03_Addressing_the_Use_Case_with_the_SAS_Language/03_Machine_Learning/03_Developing_a_Model.sasnb**","outputs":[]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Proc logselect - built the model - created the score code\n\nThe score code was created in previous steps using this type of code:\n\n```sas \nproc logselect data=work.customer_churn_ml_train_final;\n    class &char_vars &target;\n    model &target(event='1')=&char_vars &num_vars;\n    /* Specify variable selection technique*/\n    selection method=elasticnet;\n    /* Generate score code */\n    code file=\"&path/code/logscore.sas\";\nrun;\n```","outputs":[]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Score a data set using the score code from the logistic regression model","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"title2 'Score data with a %include statement referencing SAS Data Step code from proc logselect';\ndata log_scored ;\n   set churn.customer_churn_ml_test_final;\n   %include \"&path/code/logscore.sas\";\nrun;","outputs":[{"items":[{"data":"[\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2442  /** LOG_START_INDICATOR **/\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2443  title;footnote;ods _all_ close;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2444  ods graphics on;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2445  ods html5(id=vscode) style=HTMLEncore options(bitmap_mode='inline' svg_mode='inline');\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: Writing HTML5(VSCODE) Body file: sashtml112.htm\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2446  %let _SASPROGRAMFILE =\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2446! %nrquote(%nrstr(/workspaces/churnproject/sas-education/sas1/03_Addressing_the_Use_Case_with_the_SAS_Language/04_Productionizin\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2446! g_the_Model/01_Deploying_the_Model.sasnb));\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2447  title2 'Score data with a %include statement referencing SAS Data Step code from proc logselect';\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2448  data log_scored ;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2449     set churn.customer_churn_ml_test_final;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2450     %include \\\"&path/code/logscore.sas\\\";\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2606  run;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: There were 1499 observations read from the data set CHURN.CUSTOMER_CHURN_ML_TEST_FINAL.\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: The data set WORK.LOG_SCORED has 1499 observations and 32 variables.\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: DATA statement used (Total process time):\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      real time           0.00 seconds\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      cpu time            0.01 seconds\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2607  ;*';*\\\";*/;run;quit;ods html5(id=vscode) close;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2608  \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t}\n]","mime":"application/vnd.sas.compute.log.lines"}]}]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Print a few observations with the scores","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"proc sort data=log_scored ;\n    by descending P_LostCustomer ;\nrun ;\nproc print data=log_scored (obs=10) ;\n    var ID customerGender customerSubscrStat DemHomeOwner I_LostCustomer P_LostCustomer ;\nrun ;","outputs":[{"items":[{"data":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\"/>\n<meta content=\"SAS V.04.00\" name=\"generator\"/>\n<title>SAS Output</title>\n<style>\n/*<![CDATA[*/\n.body.c > table, .body.c > pre, .body.c div > table,\n.body.c div > pre, .body.c > table, .body.c > pre,\n.body.j > table, .body.j > pre, .body.j div > table,\n.body.j div > pre, .body.j > table, .body.j > pre,\n.body.c p.note, .body.c p.warning, .body.c p.error, .body.c p.fatal,\n.body.j p.note, .body.j p.warning, .body.j p.error, .body.j p.fatal,\n.body.c > table.layoutcontainer, .body.j > table.layoutcontainer { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto }\n.layoutregion.l table, .layoutregion.l pre, .layoutregion.l p.note,\n.layoutregion.l p.warning, .layoutregion.l p.error, .layoutregion.l p.fatal { margin-left: 0 }\n.layoutregion.c table, .layoutregion.c pre, .layoutregion.c p.note,\n.layoutregion.c p.warning, .layoutregion.c p.error, .layoutregion.c p.fatal { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto }\n.layoutregion.r table, .layoutregion.r pre, .layoutregion.r p.note,\n.layoutregion.r table, .layoutregion.r pre, .layoutregion.r p.note,\n.layoutregion.r p.warning, .layoutregion.r p.error, .layoutregion.r p.fatal { margin-right: 0 }\narticle, aside, details, figcaption, figure, fo