t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: There were 10 observations read from the data set WORK.GRAD_SCORED.\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"NOTE: PROCEDURE PRINT used (Total process time):\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      real time           0.01 seconds\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      cpu time            0.01 seconds\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"      \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2644  ;*';*\\\";*/;run;quit;ods html5(id=vscode) close;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"84                                                         The SAS System                       Friday, October  3, 2025 06:45:00 PM\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"title\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"title\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"2645  \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t}\n]","mime":"application/vnd.sas.compute.log.lines"}]}]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Connecting an astore model from SAS Viya Workbench to SAS Viya Model Manager\n\n*Note: Now available, see \"Transitioning the model to SAS Viya\" demonstration video in \"Lesson 6: Bridging SAS Viya Workbench and SAS Viya\".*\n\nThe astore file is downloaded for proc registermodel to access. A token is required to connect to the SAS Viya environment that is accessed via the server url.\nA new Model Manager project called myProject is created in Viya that includes all components of the gradient boosting model.\nAn example of the code structure is shown below.\n\n```sas\nproc astore;\n   download rstore = work.gbstore\n            store = \"gbstore.sasast\";\nrun;\n\n/* get token */\n%macro myTokenName() / secure;\n\"Bearer ...\"\n%mend;\n\nproc registermodel\n      name = \"gbAstore\"\n      description = \"GradBoost Astore Model\"\n      data = work.CUSTOMER_CHURN_ML_TRAIN_FINAL\n      algorithm = GRADBOOST\n      function = CLASSIFICATION\n      server = \"https://your viya server.com\"\n      oauthtoken = \"myTokenName\"\n      replace;\n   project name=\"myProject\" folder=\"myFolder\";\n   astoremodel store = \"gbstore.sasast\";\n   target LostCustomer / level=binary event=\"1\";\n   assessment;\nrun;\n```","outputs":[]}]